<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-148562" number="114216" version="2810">
			<HEADING>Chapter 6. Records and Reporting</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19442" name="T74C006"/>Chapter 6. Records and Reporting</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-148384" number="114217" version="2810">
								<HEADING>§ 6-01 Records.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19444" name="T74C006_6-01"/>§ 6-01 Records.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148383" number="114218" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>a.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Audit.</CHARFORMAT> Documents and data prepared or obtained in connection with a requirement of this title must be made reasonably available for submission to or inspection by the Director. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148382" number="114219" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>b.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Contractor and Subcontractor.</CHARFORMAT> For each Transaction subject to a Community Hiring Goal, Contractors and Subcontractors must maintain, for a period of at least 6 years from the date of completion on such Transaction, records documenting: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148381" number="114220" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>1.<TAB tab-count="1"/>publication of Employment Opportunities, if applicable; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148380" number="114221" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>2.<TAB tab-count="1"/>the Community Hires employed through referral by a Referral Source; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148379" number="114222" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>3.<TAB tab-count="1"/>labor hours performed by Community Hires in connection with the Transaction, including, but not limited to payroll records; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148378" number="114223" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>4.<TAB tab-count="1"/>efforts to meet the Community Hiring Goal, including, but not limited to, records reflecting communications with the Office of Community Hiring and Workforce Development; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148377" number="114224" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>5.<TAB tab-count="1"/>compliance with or progress towards meeting the applicable Community Hiring Goal. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148376" number="114225" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>c.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Referral Sources.</CHARFORMAT> All Referral Sources must maintain records documenting: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148375" number="114226" version="2811">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>1.<TAB tab-count="1"/>response(s) submitted to a Referral Source solicitation released pursuant to paragraph 1 of subdivision c of 74 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T74C003_3-02" destination-id="0-0-0-19418">3-02</LINK>, if applicable, for a period of at least 6 years from the date of submission; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148374" number="114227" version="2811">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>2.<TAB tab-count="1"/>authorization as a Referral Source pursuant to paragraphs 2 and 3 of subdivision c of 74 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T74C003_3-02" destination-id="0-0-0-19418">3-02</LINK>, if applicable, for a period of at least 6 years from the date of authorization; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148373" number="114228" version="2811">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>3.<TAB tab-count="1"/>for each Community Hire, services provided pursuant to 74 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T74C003_3-03" destination-id="0-0-0-19420">3-03</LINK>, for a period of at least 6 years from the date of last referral. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148372" number="114229" version="2816">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/24/24, eff. 1/23/25) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-148561" number="114230" version="2810">
								<HEADING>§ 6-02 Reporting.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19448" name="T74C006_6-02"/>§ 6-02 Reporting.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148371" number="114231" version="2811">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>a.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Community Hiring Quarterly Report.</CHARFORMAT> The Director will publish quarterly a report pursuant to subdivision c of Section <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="3502" destination-id="0-0-0-0">3502</LINK> of the Charter on a website maintained or controlled by the City. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148370" number="114232" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>1.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The report will include, for each Transaction, information demonstrating the Contractor’s and, if applicable, each Subcontractor’s progress towards meeting the applicable Community Hiring Goal. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148369" number="114233" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>2.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The report will also include, in the aggregate, information demonstrating: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148368" number="114234" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>the overall progress towards meeting the applicable Community Hiring Goal; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148367" number="114235" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>the demographics of Community Hires and, if applicable, Community Hire Apprentices; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148366" number="114236" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>the amount of compensation paid to Community Hires and, if applicable, Community Hire Apprentices, relative to the amount of compensation paid to all individuals employed by such Contractor or Subcontractor on such Transaction; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148365" number="114237" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>the total number of Community Hires employed, by type of Transaction. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148364" number="114238" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>3.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Additional Source.</CHARFORMAT> Where the Director determines that the City’s data sources are not sufficient to comply with the reporting requirements under this section, the Director may require the Contractor and, if applicable, its Subcontractor(s) to provide additional information. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148363" number="114239" version="2810">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>b.<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Annual List of Economically Disadvantaged Regions.</CHARFORMAT> The Director will annually publish, on a website maintained or controlled by the City, an updated list of Economically Disadvantaged Regions within a 100-mile radius of the City or within the metropolitan area. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-148362" number="114240" version="2816">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/24/24, eff. 1/23/25) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-104]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>